title.rendered: Luxury Car Show at Finns VIP Beach Club by Prestige Motorcars

content.rendered:
Super cars and beach vibes go together like bread and butter. We had the opportunity to work together with Finns VIP Beach Club to put together this Luxury Car Show. We brought up a great range of cars from many various brands, as well as joined by fellow car dealers from Bali. It definitely was a great and unique event, if you did not make it down to the event, please enjoy this video coverage!
